D台灣古早味蛋糕真係好撚難食 咪又係紙包蛋糕<br />\n拎去拜完山都冇人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但台灣D麵包 蛋糕係幾好食 足料 唔係空氣包 又多花款<br />\n不過D古早味蛋糕我以前路過都冇人買 台灣人自己都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前貪得意買左個咬左啖就掉左 仲要係新鮮出爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e93add43933f50c4bdd8b3c7b8e9d108ef6f63","tid":2246142,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87e31e0ce058ea98c04de12c5d0ab4229559c3cb","tid":2246142,"uid":276952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"講味其實唔差<br />\n牛油香重 幾塊餅加杯咖啡真係好撚正<br />\n但至從重拾健康 呢啲垃圾食物死撚開啦"},{"pid":"221474ffd6341e4540196a9677f9a154601bd989","tid":2246142,"uid":145118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b8be1e66b0f9259819b53884c7f415a9a0c8790","tid":2246142,"uid":344173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e202f63d99735340c02ae4f5753467798986bb71","tid":2246142,"uid":145118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31bced8b1e444a13a7bade80a066d0b3223e7dd1","tid":2246142,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"又古早<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未食過 其實有咩咁特別<br />\n<br />\n越嚟越多人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"蛋味比一般蛋糕重<br />\n同紙包蛋糕差唔多 都係咁鬆軟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"餓了，我好中意香港本土麵包店嘅紙包蛋糕，細個成日食，大個咗好少買，唔知點解。<br />\n<br />\n（順便推下post）"},{"pid":"27a36a25307615a7c1d246277c38344874190971","tid":2246142,"uid":55197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"自己整，其實唔難<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yht8Prw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i