17T00:57:10.000Z","msg":"就係普通麵包鋪曲奇<br />\n放喺蛋撻櫃十世無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n換個熊仔罐就百鳩二百蚊一盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"仲衰過普通麵包舖曲奇<br />\n<br />\n麵包舖曲奇好食好多"},{"pid":"0f8d2b26bb4ee2b8c3d7b98b95410386f84d38d4","tid":2246142,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a545c57cf1b4755ac46ed582e0e760eb10e9d8d1","tid":2246142,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:34:18.000Z","msg":"專做大陸人(遊客?)生意既小熊曲奇<br />\n而家開間古早味蛋糕<br />\n疫情，旅客幾乎為零，曲奇生意一落千丈。<br />\n轉型求生，將賣小熊曲奇的尖沙嘴店，改裝成古早味蛋糕店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4cdYUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4cdYUn.jpg&h=56ffc7d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"記得記得順手報黃藍地圖<br />\n唔係個個都追連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b178016acb07ccc40a94c225c8e60ea4a932c73","tid":2246142,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0d76168a14e9d55831c9e2b217f228685d81da3","tid":2246142,"uid":229317,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:15:18.000Z","msg":"幾年前有鬼佬客送過俾我食，話好出名！<br />\n<br />\n食左兩舊咖啡味，屙尿都有陣咖啡味，<br />\n<br />\n佢到底落左幾多增味劑！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"仲要飲咗好多水，尿都有陣咖啡味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間應該唔係呢個post講緊既鬼佬呢間"},{"pid":"81274f5fcfd28bfa7cab914eb342029aadf6252f","tid":2246142,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"專打熊仔曲奇 仲要係黃！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/86X6kQSzVPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F86X6kQSzVPc&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=031db583\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/86X6kQSzVPc</a>"},{"pid":"dc997c36f3e3e95cfb9b4b9429de3409f126c832","tid":2246142,"uid":247463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"2014年，由於珍妮曲奇大受大陸人及自由行旅客歡迎，該店推出每人每日限買兩罐曲奇餅的限購令，以遏止炒賣風氣，但持續有報道指該店店員態度惡劣，揚言「唔做香港人生意」。<br />\n<br />\n6月左右，網上開始流傳珍妮曲奇上環門市經常下半閘接待自由行，大陸旅客可以從容進出餅店購得產品，卻店員對說廣東話的顧客堅稱無貨，並拒絕本地客入內。網民曾質問餅店「問佢係咪唔做港人生意仲要話係」，並稱鄰近店舖也知悉該餅店不做香港人生意的銷售手法。"},{"pid":"b55e9ae24cebe17eb8a546b5af194adb82fd9cda","tid":2246142,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"都搵夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66ecf5b7988e3641f85fc0fa49fc67b1e0c12b3","tid":2246142,"uid":73004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11243d2715961f2535b6f1df31cab56a5a2e2e6c","tid":2246142,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ca9d85dee2a14fb9cf19ddd30b5ed8b759a9f2","tid":2246142,"uid":144811,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾食物<br />\n完。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"未食過<br />\n唔知味道點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"麵包鋪6-7蚊一舊果種清蛋糕咁，不過係熱嘅同埋淋身d，再加左芝士/朱古力咁<br />\n<br />\n新鮮出爐幾好食，不過60-70蚊又太貴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bab285de7b1e9186b9296adae3c33e952158cf","tid":2246142,"uid":230911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7995e6ba1f452f68a492dc02286098138169152","tid":2246142,"uid":40757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"1c06665fdd4d79be2a924ca06261171158b6edbf","tid":2246142,"uid":2785,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b1bb538e2388031c87a77bbdb005d986464757e3","tid":2246142,"uid":123591,"like":436,"dislike":1,"score":435,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:39:50.000Z","msg":"佢之前好串架喎 講晒出口唔做港人生意"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"邊度講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"