>\n<br />\n但當年啲人開格仔鋪 啲人又跟風又點計？<br />\n<br />\n香港從2010左右興台灣珍珠奶茶<br />\n<br />\n跟住無耐多咗好多大陸人開珍珠奶茶<br />\n<br />\n依家執返啲 覺得好咗好多<br />\n<br />\n至少一條街唔同全部都係珍奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路德圍個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係行過算鳩數（除咗茶匠）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，茶匠啲味道同包裝都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1add597da860ff6b0a53eb9dfd421d450f8583e","tid":2246142,"uid":5591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"佢嗰十幾年都賺夠啦，不要同佢宣傳下，等唔知嘅人唔好入錯去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3cff8b75d90822fd6f2ee9efcd93248ce3a498","tid":2246142,"uid":7606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"古早味蛋糕咪即係雞蛋蛋糕 賣成舊水一盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355ab4836d65ef2e74a7cc7af4d8e7492b7861f7","tid":2246142,"uid":171574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"42a857757c66c04c0bddf79cfa1b06c64dcdcfb3","tid":2246142,"uid":70915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3d659c407fd7a86464b2f9b246e6731dc9832ca","tid":2246142,"uid":118120,"like":226,"dislike":0,"score":226,"quote":{"pid":"b1bb538e2388031c87a77bbdb005d986464757e3","tid":2246142,"uid":123591,"like":436,"dislike":1,"score":435,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:39:50.000Z","msg":"佢之前好串架喎 講晒出口唔做港人生意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:17:27.000Z","msg":"要靠本地客果時就扮無野<br />\n有番遊客果時當番本地客係狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"咪囉<br />\n想當年未有遊客名氣<br />\n咪又係靠香港人起家？<br />\n以前個個男仔都係送呢個曲奇溝女"},{"pid":"cf856856a6be8a67ff724d6ef7e7dcbc987ac3b9","tid":2246142,"uid":247426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor